WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.320
Why has there been a trend towards wired headphones lately? First of all, it's practicality.

2
00:00:06.320 --> 00:00:13.600
Wired headphones have survived the eras of cassette players, CD players, MP3 players, and are still relevant today.

3
00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:20.000
Secondly, it's convenience — you don't need to charge them every day, replace the battery over time, and so on.

4
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:27.840
Thirdly, it's their data transfer speed. Wired headphones have a much lower minimum latency than wireless ones.

5
00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:33.600
That's why audiophiles, esports players, and musicians prefer to use them.
